<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08043c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08043c">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08043c"> 43(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ I saw a gun with my father ~ <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n08043c"> <li>FW unlocated</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Report of Cloonfallegh (Kiltimagh) shooting]</font>: <font color="green">[A farmer was shot and police, suspecting a neighbour, eavesdropped and collected evidence to bring him to trial.]</font> Sergeant Feely &hellip; pulling off his boots &hellip; noiselessly slipped down the kitchen chimney &hellip; The prisoner&apos;s son &hellip; deposed: &hellip; He took off his clothes and shoes and said something about Thomas Carney, that he had shot him &hellip; <mark>I saw a gun with my father</mark> &hellip; He had it since the hay-time. <small> <a name="II2jan24" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#II2jan24"><cite title="source">Irish Independent</cite></a> (2 January 1924) 5/1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
